          "content": "精神病"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "676311",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "andybon",
        "uid": "110783"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t初高中忍忍就算了 军训好像最多就一个星期 大学争取直接润出去 我见过韩国人为了躲兵役跑到国外的上学然后绿卡\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-08-04",
      "agree_count": -1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "676085",
      "is_folded": true,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "yeuoneo",
        "uid": "11686"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box collapse\" style=\"display: block;\">\n\t\t\t时时刻刻拉后腿，把教官弄得无语，为了他工作方便点，干脆让你别来了。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-08-03",
